# Range Slider

The **Range Slider** component (`rangeslider` in GH-Repo) is used on `searchpage` and `dealspage`. You can set min and max values by dragging two handles with mouse or touch. The JS component uses the library `nouislider` from [LÃ©on Gersen](https://github.com/leongersen/noUiSlider).

It consists of the slider component, a title, two input fields and an update button. The slider and the input fields get updated accordingly when you drag or insert a number manually.

